metadata.name: Points of life and death
metadata.description:
"Squeak!



Yu Can suddenly pressed down on the wooden chair and was about to jump up. "Master! What are you talking about?"



Behind him, Yuyuan put her hand on his shoulder and whispered, "Don't worry, Grandpa. Sit down first."



Yu Can sat down vacantly and looked at him with puzzled eyes. "What did you just say? The city master promised you that he would guarantee your safety?"



"Don't ask questions, Grandpa. I'll be all right, trust me." Yu Yuan whispered.
